  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Police Professionalization and Community Policing in Haut-Katanga and Kasai Oriental Provinces, Democratic Republic of the Congo &#x2013; Phase III</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To consolidate the successes of the previous project phases, this project continues to monitor the functioning and activities of security actors of the District of Kampemba (Project Phase 1) and the Southern part of the District of Annexe (Project Phase 2) in the Democratic Republic of Congo. Based on these monitoring activities, technical and logistical support is provided when needed. To improve the security of the communities in the northern part of the Annexe District, the project will adopt a holistic approach by targeting all security actors, including the communities, and by supporting the creation of structures and mechanisms aimed to better manage security in line with the community policing principles.</narrative>
  </description>
